article_id:142,category_name:Events,title_name:Facility event The Miracle of Dragonyule, coming soon!,image_path:,message:<div>The facility event The Miracle of Dragonyule will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1545026400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the flame element. You&#39;ll also be able to build event-related reward facilities!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bf82068a6bd8284528a28675423b7d4e.png"></div><div>The season of Dragonyule has arrived!</div><div><br></div><div>Yuletrees decorate the town as the people eagerly await the arrival of Saint Starfall. But wait...are those fiends here to ruin the Dragonyule festivities?!</div><div><br></div><div>Will the prince and his friends be able to reclaim their peaceful holiday?</div><div><br></div><div>And will certain characters appear in special outfits?!</div><div><br></div><div>You can find out in the next facility event... The Miracle of Dragonyule!</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2, 2-1 (Normal) of the main story to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2, 2-1 (Normal) of the main story in order to play multiplayer.</div><div>3. The event schedule and content may change without warning.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1544594400,update_time1545026475